snippet.title: Executive Update Q&A, 19th May 2021
snippet.description:
Join John Brewin, Anne-Maria Newham, and Julie Attfield as they share updates and answer your questions in this live Q&A session.

If you would prefer/need to visually see what people are saying, closed captions are available for this video. Please click ‘cc’ towards the bottom right hand side of the video.

Facilitated by Yolanda Martin, Associate Director of Communications

Featuring:
John Brewin, Chief Executive
Anne-Maria Newham, Executive Director of Nursing, AHP and Quality
Julie Attfield – Executive Director of Local Mental Health Services

Produced by Jordan Duke
Music by Bensound.com
